Front of Chemical Group, Orkem S.A., e don come out on top of Coates Brothers PLC wey be British company wey dey do ink and polyester resin.

Di state controlled Orkem don get 40.6% of Coates.

Di remaining one wey de hold by public, and by family interest, one spokeswoman for di French group yarn o.

Orkem no gree give details of di offer, instead e tok sey di British company go submit di bid for approval.

